Mzansi's newly released series Blood and Water has made it to a top spot in the US. The series, which stars an all black lead cast was launched this week on YouTube, has made it to the top ten in the US. Nosipho Dumisa, who directed it, took to Twitter to announce the good news, saying she praises God. The series stars familiar faces such as Natasha Thahane, Gail Mabalane and Nasty C with breakout starÂ Ama Qamata. This is the first ever South African series to reach this feat.  